title: [The Rift]
description: Slime and liquid drip from the close walls of the circular tunnel.  Your footing is precarious, as a rivulet runs through the area.  Low, regular thudding fills your ears, and a smell not unlike a slaughterhouse drifts in on a breeze.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, southwest
Obvious exits: north, east, southeast, southwest
